---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Jonathan O'Driscoll"
  description="Social media content, SEO blogs, online presence audits, email sequences, and more. AI-assisted content services for UK local businesses."
>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-14">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Everything you need to build an online presence that actually works. Each service is AI-assisted, fact-checked, and adapted to your brand voice.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Online Presence Audit</h2>
          <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">From £75</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A full review of your social profiles, website, Google Business Profile, and top 3 competitors. Delivered as a ranked action plan with specific recommendations you can act on immediately.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery: 24-48 hours</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Monthly Social Media Content</h2>
          <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">From £150/month</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A full month of platform-adapted posts for LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook, and TikTok. Written in your brand voice with clear CTAs. Starter (1 platform, 10 posts), Growth (2 platforms, 20 posts), or Full (4 platforms, 20 posts each).
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery: Full month's content within 72 hours of brief</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-2 border-brand-blue rounded-xl p-8 relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-3 left-8 bg-brand-blue text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">Flagship</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Authority Building Package</h2>
          <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">From £350/month</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          One SEO-targeted blog post (1,500-2,000 words, keyword-researched, optimised for Google and AI search) plus 20 social posts derived from it across platforms. Most content services do social or SEO. This does both so your content compounds over time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery: Monthly</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Content Repurposing</h2>
          <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">From £100</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Supply existing content — a YouTube video, podcast, article, or PDF — and I'll turn it into 20-30 platform-ready posts across your chosen channels. Lower creative risk, high output.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery: 48-72 hours</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Email Sequence Copywriting</h2>
          <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">From £150</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          3 to 15 email nurture or sales sequences. Written to move a subscriber from problem-aware to ready to buy. Works as a standalone product or as part of a full funnel build.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery: 5-7 days</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Short-Form Video (Script + Produced)</h2>
          <span class="text-brand-blue font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">From £150/video</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Full script written and branded video produced — ready to upload to Instagram Reels, TikTok, or YouTube Shorts. Most services give you a script. This gives you a finished video.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery: 5-7 days per video</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Not sure which to start with?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">The audit is the right first step for most businesses. It shows exactly what to prioritise before spending anything on content.</p>
      <a href="/audit" class="inline-block bg-brand-blue text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
        Get your free audit guide
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
